        {
            "title": "A股向好   銀行股揚升  四大行創近年高",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股半日微升，兩市合計成交10516.59億元(人民幣‧下同)，銀行股上揚，四大行創近年新高。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20181030_FI_A-SHARES_A股_FB-3_source-ap_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20181030_FI_A-SHARES_A股_FB-3_source-ap_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指半日升9點或0.29%，報3365點，今早以3348點開市，跌6點或0.2%，最低見3341點，跌14點或0.42%，即顯著向上，最高見3364點，升9點或0.27%。半日成交3990.11億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指半日報10804，升13點或0.13%，今早開市報10781點，亦跌9點或0.09%，其後區間波動，最低見10745點，跌46點或0.43%，最高見10817，升26點或0.24%，半日成交6526.48億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數半日收報10804，升13點或0.13%，今早跌4點或0.12%，開報3942點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數半日跌1點或0.09%，報2224點，今早開市報2223點，跌3點或0.14%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">銀行股揚升，工商銀行(601398.SH)升2.16%，報7.11元、中國銀行(601988.SH)升2.39%，報5.57元、建設銀行(601939.SH)升1.26%，報8.85元，及農業銀行(601288.SH)升1.72%，報5.33元，齊創新高。齊魯銀行(601665.SH)升4.84%，報6.07元，中信銀行(滬:601998)揚2.59%，報6.74元、招商銀行(600036.SH)升1.41%，報42.39元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14714118-a%e8%82%a1%e5%90%91%e5%a5%bd-%e9%8a%80%e8%a1%8c%e8%82%a1%e6%8f%9a%e5%8d%87-%e5%9b%9b%e5%a4%a7%e8%a1%8c%e5%89%b5%e8%bf%91%e5%b9%b4%e9%ab%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_A-SHARE_5_source-ap_-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-18 11:45:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "龍蟠科技A、H齊揚 在港股價曾飆逾30%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">半新股龍蟠科技(02465)今早A、H齊揚，在港掛牌的H股一度衝上5.94元，升30.84%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：龍蟠科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241021_FI_source-web_Lopal.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：龍蟠科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241021_FI_source-web_Lopal.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：龍蟠科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">龍蟠科技A股(603906.SH)今早裂口造好，初段已升約10%漲停板；其後該公司H股升勢進一步提升，升越30%後才略為回吐。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至上午約11時16分，該股報5.68元，升幅收窄至25.11%，成交1.94億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14713994-%e9%be%8d%e8%9f%a0%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80a%e3%80%81h%e9%bd%8a%e6%8f%9a-%e5%9c%a8%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e6%9b%be%e9%a3%86%e9%80%be30",
