        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段稍彈 恒指回升48點報22664點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段略為反彈，恒生指數開市報22664點，升48點或0.21%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5519點，升19點或0.36%；國企指數以8343點開市，升20點或0.24%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-ap_China_Tencent_Group-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-ap_China_Tencent_Group-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股升多跌少，昨天支撐大市的騰訊(00700)，今早開報494.2元，微升0.12%；阿里巴巴(09988)開報122元，微跌0.16%；美團(03690)開報170.2元，升0.77%；京東(09618)開報158.3元，也升0.76%；小米(01810)開報45.15元，暫時無升跌。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">將於明天中午公布業績的滙控(00005)，今早開報86.15元，升0.76%；同系恒生銀行(00011)開報105元，暫時無升跌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240430_FI_source-web_00005-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240430_FI_source-web_00005-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今日收市後派成績表的百度(09888)，股份經昨天顯著調整後，今早開報90.05元，微升0.22%；今日中午公布業績的希慎興業(00014)則以12.04元開市，暫時無升跌。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">譚仔國際(02217)獲提私有化，作價較停牌前收市價有高達75.56%溢價；該股今早復牌應聲彈升，開報1.48元，較停牌前升64.44%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：譚仔國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230814_FI_source-web_02217.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：譚仔國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230814_FI_source-web_02217.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：譚仔國際官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">京信通信(02342)發新股引入易磊及英特爾為股東，作價僅較昨天收市價折讓1.8%；該股今早顯著造好，開報1.24元，漲11.71%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14713649-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e7%a8%8d%e5%bd%88-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%8748%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b122664%e9%bb%9e",
